        "description": "Create a new worker with user account.\n\n**Authentication:** Required (COMPANY role)\n\n**Request Body:**\n- name (string, required): 2-100 characters\n- initials (string, optional): Max 10 characters\n- telephone (string, optional): Max 20 characters\n- mobile (string, optional): Max 20 characters\n- email (string, optional): Valid email format, max 100 characters\n- username (string, required): 3-20 characters (for worker login)\n- password (string, required): Minimum 8 characters\n\n**Business Logic:**\n- Creates both Worker entity and User account with ROLE_WORKER\n- Worker is associated with the company of the authenticated user\n- Username must be unique across all users\n- Email must be unique if provided\n\n**Response:**\n- id (long): Worker ID\n- name (string): Worker name\n- initials (string): Initials\n- telephone (string): Telephone number\n- mobile (string): Mobile number\n- email (string): Email address\n- username (string): Login username\n- loginLocked (boolean): Account lock status\n- archived (boolean): Archive status\n- createdAt (datetime): Creation timestamp\n- updatedAt (datetime): Last update timestamp"
      },
