        "description": "Invite a new worker by email. Creates an invitation record and sends an email with a unique verification token.\n\n**Authentication:** Required (COMPANY role)\n\n**Request Body:**\n- email (string, required): Worker's email address\n- firstName (string, required): Worker's first name\n- lastName (string, required): Worker's last name\n\n**Response:**\n- id (long): Invitation ID\n- companyId (long): Company ID\n- email (string): Worker's email\n- firstName (string): Worker's first name\n- lastName (string): Worker's last name\n- status (string): Invitation status (PENDING)\n- token (string): Unique verification token (for testing only, not sent in production)\n- expiresAt (datetime): Token expiration timestamp (7 days from creation)\n- createdAt (datetime): Invitation creation timestamp\n\n**Business Logic:**\n- Generates unique verification token valid for 7 days\n- Sends invitation email with signup link containing token\n- Token can be used for worker signup\n- Only one pending invitation per email allowed\n\n**Status Code:** 201 Created\n\n**Error Responses:**\n- 400 Bad Request: Invalid email or missing required fields\n- 409 Conflict: Active invitation already exists for this email"
